      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and use. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, small door dings, and some fading on the clear coat, while the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and carpet. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it will likely need some routine maintenance soon, such as new brake pads and a suspension tune-up. It is a solid choice for someone looking for affordable transportation who doesn't mind a bit of character and some DIY upkeep.",
