    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total dream. This car is in truly mint condition\u2014it looks and drives just like it did the day I picked it up from the dealership! I\u2019ve babied this ride since day one, so you're getting something that\u2019s been loved and kept in flawless shape. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Come say hi and take a look!",
      "price": 43900.0,
