    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade Mazda RX-7 FD, powered by the legendary 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine. This specimen exhibits exceptional health with verified high-compression numbers across all rotor faces and a meticulously maintained cooling system to prevent thermal degradation. The drivetrain features the original five-speed manual transmission with precise gate engagement and a Torsen limited-slip differential. The chassis retains its factory-engineered 50/50 weight distribution, supported by an untouched double-wishbone suspension setup and pristine subframe integrity. Free of vacuum leaks or boost fluctuations, this vehicle offers a pure, analog driving experience in an aesthetically and mechanically flawless state.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_3",
