    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade example that redefines the standard for excellence. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, shielded from the elements since day one. The exterior finish remains in showroom condition, boasting a deep, mirror-like luster enhanced by a professional-grade ceramic coating; there are absolutely no stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings to be found. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new, with the premium leather seating surfaces showing zero bolster wear and the carpets protected by original factory mats. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the intuitive navigation suite, functions with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, accompanied by a comprehensive service portfolio documenting every scheduled maintenance interval performed exclusively at authorized dealerships. This sale includes all original keys, the factory window sticker, and a custom-fitted indoor car cover. For the discerning buyer who demands perfection without compromise, this vehicle offers a rare opportunity to own a piece of automotive history in its purest form.",
      "price": 48500.0,
